{"title":"孩子们的诗","authors":["李富祺"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李富祺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨露"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨晚我做了一个梦——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群孩子坐着小船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划呀划到银河两旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把天上的星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都摘进了船舱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天早上醒来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星果然不见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知是谁把它挂满树上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧，一片片叶子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是有一颗颗星儿在闪亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿，你为啥这样调皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢滑落在村前的树梢上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道不怕弟弟用竹竿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——把你捅落池塘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿，你怎么那样大胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自跳进河里游荡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不怕弟弟把你捉住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——往鱼篓里装？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，月儿神秘地睁圆眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄凑近我的耳旁："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“现在弟弟讲文明懂礼貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱和他捉迷藏！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴一滴的汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多象书本上的标点符号——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚冒出来的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是倒挂的逗号；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往下滴落的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是连续的叹号；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在地上的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是一个个句号……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动，它是一首动人的赞歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水不就是闪光的标点符号！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}